{"tid":165853,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"想學小提琴 自學可唔可行?","createTime":"2017-03-21T16:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T09:12:41.000Z","uid":86549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ca0b77aa91b69661466b2bfa28a80ce4a1ca155","tid":165853,"uid":86549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:11:53.000Z","msg":"定係出出面學<br />\n好耐冇掂過音樂 應該點入手 出去學既去邊學好?"},{"pid":"b5db8cdac6929c67cde2b2ca66157772bf6ea74d","tid":165853,"uid":93126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:31:46.000Z","msg":"新手去普通琴行學都已經可以，都係最基本一把位學起，學下好簡單嘰歌(當初小星星係我第一首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)所以唔洗話要好勁果d老師架。覺得去琴行7可以上幾堂問下佢上唔上門教(其實你可以上網/搵fd介紹，真係求其都得)<br />\n再學高級d，覺得琴行個老師好可以繼續跟，問下佢上唔上門教/甚至叫佢介紹其他老師佢都應該唔會介意。<br />\n自學實得架，但小提琴真係好難，因為比鋼琴更多技巧要學!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 運弓技巧、震音、轉把點轉得自然又快etc (除非你話你只係玩玩下，唔洗拉得好聽)<br />\n加油，希望幫到你，小提琴真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 純個人經驗 <br />\nbtw小提琴學緊演奏級，有玩過出面樂團"},{"pid":"f96debfa597a1d7930bd5479b368126e263ec3f4","tid":165853,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:35:07.000Z","msg":"學緊八級，唔建議自學，因為有人教都好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc26b877249106b74608cdfa1e3315216bdf8e9","tid":165853,"uid":86549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:37:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手去普通琴行學都已經可以，都係最基本一把位學起，學下好簡單嘰歌(當初小星星係我第一首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)所以唔洗話要好勁果d老師架。覺得去琴行7可以上幾堂問下佢上唔上門教(其實你可以上網/搵fd介紹，真係求其都得)<br />\n再學高級d，覺得琴行個老師好可以繼續跟，問下佢上唔上門教/甚至叫佢介紹其他老師佢都應該唔會介意。<br />\n自學實得架，但小提琴真係好難，因為比鋼琴更多技巧要學!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 運弓技巧、震音、轉把點轉得自然又快etc (除非你話你只係玩玩下，唔洗拉得好聽)<br />\n加油，希望幫到你，小提琴真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 純個人經驗 <br />\nbtw小提琴學緊演奏級，有玩過出面樂團</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打收唔收學生<br />\n去琴行學幾錢一個月先算抵<br />\n我遲D得閒練會多D時間 想學快D<br />\n想拉得好聽 幾年內考到5級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58e50071e03ce75bb5df2dd64fa8f720b977f42","tid":165853,"uid":72948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"想搵小提琴老師可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教左十幾年琴，係港島東教"},{"pid":"2c7dfbe61d9a2cdbf0ca3e0b58a6f2e22c9035be","tid":165853,"uid":86549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:39:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想搵小提琴老師可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教左十幾年琴，係港島東教</blockquote><br />\n有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇TG?"},{"pid":"43b4bbd49ffff9a7a5cf333cac3b676dc4950d17","tid":165853,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:39:16.000Z","msg":"自學唔可行.<br />\n有好多野好&quot;抽象&quot; , 有時睇片睇字都未必明.<br />\nVibrato已經夠你玩幾堂.<br />\n<br />\n利: 教左十年 初學到8級"},{"pid":"d9edc422d3e31a71fa4914e9693ae487dfebbb49","tid":165853,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:39:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想搵小提琴老師可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教左十幾年琴，係港島東教</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊間呀? <br />\n利: 同行同區"},{"pid":"716c64a5645a7996aa538a5aef65ac79fee85e19","tid":165853,"uid":72948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想搵小提琴老師可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教左十幾年琴，係港島東教</blockquote><br />\n有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇TG?</blockquote><br />\n無TG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g