s/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f913f632a8c9d6f7825bfc2eeeffd40f6f2658c","tid":165853,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想搵小提琴老師可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教左十幾年琴，係港島東教</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊間呀? <br />\n利: 同行同區</blockquote><br />\n全私教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打你呢？</blockquote><br />\n開琴行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾銀一堂?</blockquote><br />\n上網睇到佘詩曼巴打好撚型."},{"pid":"b7b6f30f38a6f993a13af211825f1a5361ebab44","tid":165853,"uid":72948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:49:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想搵小提琴老師可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教左十幾年琴，係港島東教</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊間呀? <br />\n利: 同行同區</blockquote><br />\n全私教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打你呢？</blockquote><br />\n開琴行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾銀一堂?</blockquote><br />\n上網睇到佘詩曼巴打好撚型.</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1de9621c64def62995ef821b566bdb2fac9a74","tid":165853,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:49:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新手去普通琴行學都已經可以，都係最基本一把位學起，學下好簡單嘰歌(當初小星星係我第一首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)所以唔洗話要好勁果d老師架。覺得去琴行7可以上幾堂問下佢上唔上門教(其實你可以上網/搵fd介紹，真係求其都得)<br />\n再學高級d，覺得琴行個老師好可以繼續跟，問下佢上唔上門教/甚至叫佢介紹其他老師佢都應該唔會介意。<br />\n自學實得架，但小提琴真係好難，因為比鋼琴更多技巧要學!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 運弓技巧、震音、轉把點轉得自然又快etc (除非你話你只係玩玩下，唔洗拉得好聽)<br />\n加油，希望幫到你，小提琴真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 純個人經驗 <br />\nbtw小提琴學緊演奏級，有玩過出面樂團</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打收唔收學生<br />\n去琴行學幾錢一個月先算抵<br />\n我遲D得閒練會多D時間 想學快D<br />\n想拉得好聽 幾年內考到5級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔收，因為個人太摺唔係好識同人溝通同教人，唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真，去琴行學就算平都唔會平得去邊，因為會抽傭(所以先叫你搵fd介紹或者上網搵 應該一級就150-200蚊堂掛，not sure，l太耐歷史啦)我果時細細個琴行都收緊成千銀1粒鐘4堂<br />\n勤力1年-年半都考到5級!!!!(認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)勤力係指緊每日抽1個鐘above練琴，認真咁練，都明白d歌/basic野好悶，但絕對值!特別上到高級就會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定唔洗1000蚊4堂啦.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f24b800d28d0a9b1c71c413440eea40bba8b0d","tid":165853,"uid":86549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:51:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新手去普通琴行學都已經可以，都係最基本一把位學起，學下好簡單嘰歌(當初小星星係我第一首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)所以唔洗話要好勁果d老師架。覺得去琴行7可以上幾堂問下佢上唔上門教(其實你可以上網/搵fd介紹，真係求其都得)<br />\n再學高級d，覺得琴行個老師好可以繼續跟，問下佢上唔上門教/甚至叫佢介紹其他老師佢都應該唔會介意。<br />\n自學實得架，但小提琴真係好難，因為比鋼琴更多技巧要學!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 運弓技巧、震音、轉把點轉得自然又快etc (除非你話你只係玩玩下，唔洗拉得好聽)<br />\n加油，希望幫到你，小提琴真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 純個人經驗 <br />\nbtw小提琴學緊演奏級，有玩過出面樂團</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打收唔